# shelchemy - Dict-like (shelve-like) storage wrapper for any DBMS (SQLAlchemy)
 


## Python installation
### from package
```bash
# Set up a virtualenv. 
python3 -m venv venv
source venv/bin/activate

# Install from PyPI
pip install shelchemy
```

### from source
```bash
git clone https://github.com/shelchemy/shelchemy
cd shelchemy
poetry install
```

